Class SystemAppRegistrar

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.lucidworks.apollo.component.SystemAppRegistrar

  • public class SystemAppRegistrar
extends java.lang.Object
    Creates system app that will link all system objects to prevent them from being deleted by cascade deletes. Creates shared group that holds system objects that could be added to customer apps
